  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Take a journey through the Fjords, starting from the World Heritage city of </span><a data-udi="umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/bergen" title="Bergen">Bergen</a><span> and ending in the capital city of </span><a data-udi="umb://document/4c3abf6ce2194dfe8f13f1fea46fd3d5" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/oslo" title="Oslo">Oslo</a><span>. Travel on panoramic trains, ferries and railways to really experience the breath-taking nature that Norway has to offer. Being able to experience one of the most picturesque rail journeys in the world, the Fl</span><span>å</span><span>m Railway, is a real highlight of this tour. </span></p>
<div>
<p><strong>Maximum Group Size: </strong>25</p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/bergen-to-oslo-fjord-experience#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/bergen-to-oslo-fjord-experience#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/bergen-to-oslo-fjord-experience#Your holiday Includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/bergen-to-oslo-fjord-experience#Hotels">Hotels </a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/bergen-to-oslo-fjord-experience#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
